summary: GO collab update: Turn In Your Arms
title: GO collab update: Turn In Your Arms
body:
by @irisbleufic & @procrastinatingbookworm

#2 / 8: WEDNESDAY, 20 AUGUST 1997

[Tam Lin retelling; rated M.  Updates daily till done.]

*

Aziraphale handed the book to Crowley and fished a notebook out of his coat pocket. He didn’t remember bringing along a pen, but suddenly there was one. He flipped through the notebook until he found the page, and wrote angelic form? underneath serpent.

“There’s also that…thing.” Crowley gestured. “Maggoty thing. You might get an armful of that.”

Aziraphale forced himself not to shudder and wrote that down, too. Desperate times indeed.

summary: as the Good Omens fandom starts to pick up in advance of the miniseries, i’ve been seeing people tag Aziraphale/Crowley...
body: as the Good Omens fandom starts to pick up in advance of the miniseries, i’ve been seeing people tag Aziraphale/Crowley as “ineffable husbands”, which is fine and good but also wtf happened to “air conditioning”. you know, the natural expansion of “a/c”? that’s the kind of good old-fashioned inscrutable ship-naming for which I, personally, am here. what sort of coward directly references the actual text.

summary: New GO collab: Turn In Your Arms
title: New GO collab: Turn In Your Arms
body:
by @irisbleufic & @procrastinatingbookworm

#1 / 8: TUESDAY, 19 AUGUST 1997

[Tam Lin retelling; rated M.  Updates daily till done.]

*

Slow-dawning horror was all that Aziraphale could process, not least because his eyes had finally fallen on the lines most relevant. Holding onto a shapeshifter wasn’t so difficult for their sort, and hadn’t he been doing it for thousands of years? No, the catch was—

“There will always be consequences, angel,” Crowley said, low and pained. “Sometimes the stories are true.”

title: FANFICTION TROPES
body:
Soulmate au requested by @phen0l

 you aCTUALLY REQUESTED IT!!!!

Levi/Reader or Eren/Reader. Probably would 85% write it. I haven’t exactly figured out how the entire plot would go but the gist of it would be like:

I have been reincarnated many times. We both have actually, and we fell in love for just as many. The rings we wore, gold, silver, bronze, and at some point a piece of string when we were too poor to afford it, and I still loved you.

Sinbad/Reader. 100% would write it and currently making one cause I love Shitbad. I have an idea and it would probably be based on something like this:

“There are two certainties in this world: love and death, and death we have not.”

“And sometimes not even love.”

“No. Always love. You have seen it. You have given it. You have blessed it,” he pauses. “Surely, you must know how to love.”

Guren/Reader. 50% would write this bECAUSE I COULD USE THIS IDEA IVE BEEN MEANING TO USE:

“What’s the difference between the love of your life and a soulmate?”

“One’s a choice and the other is not.”

Crowley/Reader. 65% would write it cause apparently, I need to catch up on ONS and I have a hard time writing this bab cause like,,,, I haven’t really studied his character well??? But I have an idea and it’d go as something like:

“I don’t even know how to love.”

“But, I can teach you how to love.”
